<br>
We aren't balanced, and none of the wizards I speak with daily disagree with this.  The possible exception to this would be those wizards who actively participate/create AE groups.  I see a fair number of posts concerning AE groups, but in reality (on Brell at least), the majority of the community doesnt seem be able to grow beyond the first tactics they learned.<br>
<br>
